Tis’ the season for savings and prizesTis’ the season for savings and prizes
Mechanics:
1. Promo period is from 16 October 2023 – 15 January 2024
2. Open to all Sabre-connected Travel Agencies nationwide.
3. Exclusive Asiana Airlines (OZ) fares will be available in the Sabre system.
4. Book and ticket with Asiana Airlines (OZ) within the promo period using the Sabre
system to qualify.
5. A travel agency (Sabre PCC) must have confirmed OZ segments booked in Sabre to
qualify.
6. Travel Agencies with confirmed OZ segments during the promo period earn raffle points.
1 segment = 1 point.
7. Entries within the promotion period will be tracked automatically.
8. Winners shall be notified via email and personal call from Sabre.
9. List of winners will be posted on Sabre Philippines social media pages.
10. Sabre and Asiana Airlines reserve the right to amend the conditions and period
of this promotion.
11. Decisions of Sabre and Asiana Airlines on all matters relating to this
promotion will be final and binding.
